1. Update and upgrade your Pi
apt update && upgrade
2. Install Python 3.9 & pip
apt install python3 $$ python3-pip

3. Install Git
apt install git

4. Download the source code for this project
git clone https://github.com/ripsys/power_consumer.git

5. Install the Python dependencies for the source code
pip install influxdb
pip install spidev
pip install scipy

Install a specific kernel known to not exhibit the known SPI sampling rate issues.
